items.name: Smart_Fire_Detection_Evacuation_System
items.description: Smart Fire Detection and Evacuation Assistant is an ESP32-based IoT system that detects fire, smoke, gas leakage, and abnormal temperature early. It alerts occupants, controls ventilation and exits, estimates trapped people, and sends email alerts to fire services for quick response.

items.name: PEST-DECTECTION-AND-MITIGATION
items.description: AI-based computer vision system for real-time agricultural pest detection using YOLOv5-Nano, YOLOv8-Nano, and YOLOv11-Nano. Trained on the IP102 dataset with strong augmentation for robust field performance. Outputs pest bounding boxes, labels, and confidence scores.
